text: Vasiliy Kondratenko (born 2 September 1989) is a Russian bobsledder. He competed in the two-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Russia Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
